TITLE: Transaction State Error Handling
DESCRIPTION: Advanced error handling using transaction state and retry logic
SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/advanced/entity-manager.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$manager = new \Cycle\ORM\EntityManager($orm);
$manager->persist($entity);
$state = $manager->run(throwException: false);

while ($error = $state->getLastError()) {
    if ($error instanceof \Cycle\Database\Exception\StatementException\ConnectionException) {
        usleep(100);
        $state->retry();
        continue;
    }

    throw $error;
}
```

