TITLE: Adding User Values to ON Statements with onWhere Method
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to include user values in ON statements using onWhere, orOnWhere, and andOnWhere methods. The example joins the 'users' table with conditions based on both column relationships and literal values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/database/query-builders.md#2025-04-20_snippet_41

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$select
    ->innerJoin('users')
    ->on(['users.id' => 'test.id'])
