SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/database/query-builders.md#2025-04-20_snippet_47

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$select->join('LEFT', 'photos', 'pht', [
    'pht.user_id' => 'users.id',
    'users.is_admin' => 'pht.is_admin',
    static function (
        \Cycle\Database\Query\SelectQuery $select,
        string $boolean,
        callable $wrapper
    ): void {
        $select
            ->on('photos.user_id', 'users.id')
            ->onWhere('photos.type', 'avatar');
    }
]);
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT *
FROM `users`
         LEFT JOIN `photos` AS `pht`
                   ON (
                               `pht`.`user_id` = `users`.`id`
                           AND
                               `users`.`is_admin` = `pht`.`is_admin`
                           AND
                               (`photos`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` AND `photos`.`type` = "avatar")
                       )
```

