LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
class NewFieldMigration extends Migration
{
    public function up()
    {
        $this->table('sample_table')
            ->addColumn('field', 'float')
            ->update();
    }

    public function down()
    {
        $this->table('sample_table')
            ->dropColumn('field')
            ->update();
    }
}
```

