TITLE: Adding Command Chain Sequence in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to chain multiple commands together using the Special\Sequence command. This allows executing additional commands after the main operation completes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/mapper/extending.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Cycle\ORM\Command;
use Cycle\ORM\Heap;

public function queueCreate(object $entity, Heap\Node $node, Heap\State $state): Command\CommandInterface
{
