TITLE: Custom Runner Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a custom runner with logging capabilities
SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/advanced/entity-manager.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
class LogRunner implements RunnerInterface
{
    private RunnerInterface $runner;

    public function __construct(
        private LoggerInterface $logger
    ) {
        $this->runner = new \Cycle\ORM\Transaction\Runner();
    }

    public function run(CommandInterface $command): void
    {
        $this->logger->debug($command);

        $this->runner->run($command);
    }

    public function complete(): void
    {
        $this->runner->complete();
    }

    public function rollback(): void
    {
        $this->runner->rollback();
    }
}
```

