TITLE: Custom Collection Factory Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a custom collection factory by implementing CollectionFactoryInterface.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cycle/docs/blob/2.x/docs/en/relation/collections.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Cycle\ORM\Collection\CollectionFactoryInterface;

class ArrayCollectionFactory implements CollectionFactoryInterface
{
    public function withCollectionClass(string $class): static
    {
        // Do nothing
        return $this;
    }

    public function collect(iterable $data): array
    {
        return match (true) {
            \is_array($data) => $data,
            $data instanceof \Traversable => \iterator_to_array($data),
            default => throw new CollectionFactoryException('Unsupported iterable type.'),
        };
    }
}
```

